<TEI.2><text lang="greek"><body><div1 type="choral" org="uniform" sample="complete"><div2 type="strophe" n="4" org="uniform" sample="complete"><sp><p><milestone ed="p" n="1008" unit="card" /></p></sp></div2>
<div2 type="antistrophe" n="4" org="uniform" sample="complete">
<sp><speaker>Ξέρξης</speaker><p>
<lb />πεπλήγμεθ᾽ οἵᾳ δι᾽ αἰῶνος  τύχᾳ:</p></sp>
<sp><speaker>Χορός</speaker><p>
<lb />πεπλήγμεθ᾽: εὔδηλα  γάρ:</p></sp>
<sp><speaker>Ξέρξης</speaker><p>
<lb rend="displayNum" n="1010" />νέᾳ νέᾳ δύᾳ  δύᾳ.</p></sp>
<sp><speaker>Χορός</speaker><p>
<lb rend="displayNum" n="1012" />κύρσαντες οὐκ  εὐτυχῶς
<lb rend="displayNum" n="1011" />Ἰάνων ναυβατᾶν.
<lb rend="displayNum" n="1013" />δυσπόλεμον δὴ γένος τὸ  Περσᾶν.
</p></sp></div2></div1></body></text></TEI.2>